<HEAD>Italian Porn Star Cicciolina Arrested For Indecent Exposure</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BRUSSELS, Belgium (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Italian porn star and parliamentarian
Ilona Staller was arrested for indecent exposure today after
performing a striptease at a bar and mingling too liberally with
the customers, police said.
   Staller, better known as Cicciolina, was being questioned by
police.
   Staller arrived in the Belgian capital Friday to launch her bid
for a seat in the European Parliament in the 1989 elections and to
speak out in favor of sexual liberty.
   She had scheduled several shows here and in nearby Charleroi.
   Between 200 and 300 people attended her show at the Canal Street
nightclub, including some Brussels police officers.
   Before Staller arrived, police had warned she would be arrested
if her behavior was unacceptable by Belgian standards.
   A police spokesman said while striptease is not illegal in
Belgium, Staller overstepped the bounds of decency when she left
the night club stage and began mingling with the audience.
   Staller was elected to the Italian Parliament last year as a
candidate for the small, outspoken Radical Party.
